description:
Jessica Parsons from Netlify gives an update on Netlify Build Plugins and some of the partners such as Algolia, Nimbella and Snyk that have recently launched new build plugins and integrations.

Presented by Jessica Parsons, Product Manager, Netlify - https://twitter.com/VeryThorough | https://www.verythorough.com/

Brought to you by Netlify (netlify.com) - Jamstack Conf Virtual 2020 https://jamstackconf.com
title: Netlify Partner Integrations
